{"id":935,"parent_id":934,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":935,"title":"Nahum 1","subtitle":"","short_title":"Nahum","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1","content":[["div",[".title",["span.dominant","Nahum"]],[".titleNumber","Chapter 1"],[".studySummary",["i","Nahum speaks of the burning of the earth at the Second Coming and of the mercy and power of the Lord."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.1","order":"02.35.001.62181"},["b","1"],"The burden of Nineveh. The book of the vision of Nahum the Elkoshite."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.2","order":"02.35.001.62182"},["b","2"],"God",["i","is"],"jealous, and the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"revengeth; the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"revengeth, and",["i","is"],"furious; the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"will take vengeance on his adversaries, and he reserveth",["i","wrath"],"for his enemies."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.3","order":"02.35.001.62183"},["b","3"],"The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","is"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"slow to anger"],", and great in power, and will not at all acquit",["i","the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"wicked"],":"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","hath"],"his way in the whirlwind and in the storm, and the clouds",["i","are"],"the dust of his feet."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.4","order":"02.35.001.62184"},["b","4"],"He rebuketh the sea, and maketh it dry, and drieth up all the rivers: Bashan languisheth, and Carmel, and the flower of Lebanon languisheth."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.5","order":"02.35.001.62185"},["b","5"],"The mountains quake at him, and the hills",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"melt"],", and the earth is",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"burned"],"at his",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"presence"],", yea, the world, and all that dwell therein."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.6","order":"02.35.001.62186"},["b","6"],"Who can stand before his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"indignation"],"? and who can abide in the fierceness of his anger? his fury is poured out like fire, and the rocks are thrown down by him."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.7","order":"02.35.001.62187"},["b","7"],"The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","is"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"good"],", a strong hold in the day of trouble; and he knoweth them that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"trust"],"in him."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.8","order":"02.35.001.62188"},["b","8"],"But with an overrunning flood he will make an utter end of the place thereof, and darkness shall pursue his enemies."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.9","order":"02.35.001.62189"},["b","9"],"What do ye imagine against the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"? he will make an utter end: affliction shall not rise up the second time."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.10","order":"02.35.001.62190"},["b","10"],"For while",["i","they be"],"folden together",["i","as"],"thorns, and while they are drunken",["i","as"],"drunkards, they shall be devoured as",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"stubble"],"fully dry."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.11","order":"02.35.001.62191"},["b","11"],"There is",["i","one"],"come out of thee, that imagineth evil against the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", a wicked counsellor."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.12","order":"02.35.001.62192"},["b","12"],"Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; Though",["i","they be"],"quiet, and likewise many, yet thus shall they be cut down, when he shall pass through. Though I have afflicted thee, I will afflict thee no more."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.13","order":"02.35.001.62193"},["b","13"],"For now will I break his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"yoke"],"from off thee, and will burst thy bonds in sunder."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.14","order":"02.35.001.62194"},["b","14"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath given a commandment concerning thee,",["i","that"],"no more of thy name be sown: out of the house of thy gods will I cut off the graven image and the molten image: I will make thy grave; for thou art vile."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.15","order":"02.35.001.62195"},["b","15"],"Behold upon the mountains the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"feet"],"of him that bringeth good tidings, that publisheth peace! O Judah, keep thy solemn feasts, perform thy vows: for the wicked shall no more pass through thee; he is utterly cut off."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.3a","order":"02.35.001.62196"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/forbear"},"TG Forbear"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.3b","order":"02.35.001.62198"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/34.7"},"Ex. 34:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/4.5"},"Morm. 4:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.9"},"D&C 1:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.5a","order":"02.35.001.62200"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/97.5"},"Ps. 97:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.5b","order":"02.35.001.62202"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.66"},"D&C 101:66"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/earth-cleansing-of"},"TG Earth, Cleansing of"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.5c","order":"02.35.001.62204"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-presence-of"},"TG God, Presence of"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.6a","order":"02.35.001.62206"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-indignation-of"},"TG God, Indignation of"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.7a","order":"02.35.001.62208"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/34.8"},"Ps. 34:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/3.25"},"Lam. 3:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/70.18.17-18"},"D&C 70:18 (17–18)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.7b","order":"02.35.001.62210"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/faith"},"TG Faith"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.10a","order":"02.35.001.62212"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/26.6.4-6"},"2 Ne. 26:6 (4–6)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/29.9"},"D&C 29:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.37"},"JS—H 1:37"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.13a","order":"02.35.001.62214"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/bondage-physical"},"TG Bondage, Physical"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/1.15a","order":"02.35.001.62216"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.15"},"Rom. 10:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/15.18.13-18"},"Mosiah 15:18 (13–18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/20.40"},"3 Ne. 20:40"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/128.19"},"D&C 128:19"],"."]]}
